280
00:14:52,725 --> 00:14:57,771
<c.ms Gothic>（木人）そうして花となった命が</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>丹の源となる</c.ms Gothic>

281
00:14:58,272 --> 00:15:00,149
<c.ms Gothic>あくまで言い伝えでしょ</c.ms Gothic>

282
00:15:00,232 --> 00:15:02,568
<c.ms Gothic>額面通りには受け取れないわねぇ</c.ms Gothic>

283
00:15:02,651 --> 00:15:05,821
<c.ms Gothic>（木人）不老不死の仙薬は実在する</c.ms Gothic>

284
00:15:06,405 --> 00:15:09,199
<c.ms Gothic>私も恩恵の一部を受けている</c.ms Gothic>

285
00:15:10,159 --> 00:15:11,702
<c.ms Gothic>再生した！</c.ms Gothic>

286
00:15:12,286 --> 00:15:15,164
<c.ms Gothic>（佐切）先ほども千年生きていると</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>言っていましたが</c.ms Gothic>

287
00:15:16,540 --> 00:15:17,917
<c.ms Gothic>その娘も同じなのか？</c.ms Gothic>

288
00:15:18,000 --> 00:15:20,085
<c.ms Gothic>（泣きそうな声）</c.ms Gothic>

289
00:15:20,169 --> 00:15:22,463
<c.ms Gothic>（佐切）ちょ…</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>刀で人を指さない！</c.ms Gothic>

290
00:15:22,546 --> 00:15:23,505
<c.ms Gothic>えっ？</c.ms Gothic>

291
00:15:23,589 --> 00:15:25,799
<c.ms Gothic>うわぁ～</c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>　</c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>引くわぁ～</c.ms Gothic>

292
00:15:25,883 --> 00:15:28,218
<c.ms Gothic>そう？</c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>　</c.ms Gothic><c.ms Gothic>ごめん</c.ms Gothic>

293
00:15:28,302 --> 00:15:32,932
<c.ms Gothic>信じようと信じまいと</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>ここは神仙郷</c.ms Gothic>

294
00:15:33,015 --> 00:15:36,477
<c.ms Gothic>立ち入った人間がどうなるかは</c.ms Gothic>
<c.ms Gothic>神の意思</c.ms Gothic>

295
00:15:36,560 --> 00:15:40,564
<c.ms Gothic>（木人）島を出るのも</c.ms Gothic>
